To install docker edge release (edge nothing but beeta version)
    Edge is released monthly and supported for a month.

    Stable is released quarterly and support for 4 months
curl -sSL https://get.docker.com/ | sh
download docker for store.docker.com

installing docker
need to install docker-machine and docker-compose 


https://docs.docker.com/machine/install-machine/

curl -L https://github.com/docker/machine/releases/download/v0.13.0/docker-machine-`uname -s`-`uname -m` >/tmp/docker-machine &&
chmod +x /tmp/docker-machine &&
sudo cp /tmp/docker-machine /usr/local/bin/docker-machine


https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/

sudo curl -L https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.16.1/docker-compose-`uname -s`-`uname -m` -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose

Otherway to get docker compose file is from github.com
github.com/docker/compose/releases
github.com/docker/machine/releases

